                  <summary><p>The palm-leaf bundle, a composite manuscript, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Viratam Iraṇṭu</title> on its additional title page, contains:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Citamparacakkaram</title> (Indien 6a).</item>
  <item>A list of personal names and dates (Indien 6b).</item>
  <item>A stanza (Indien 6c).</item>
  </list></p>
   <p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (October 2020).</p>  <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
                  
